title: heya summoners !
body:

replies.body:
Welcome to the Oceania server! You'll find that it's probably a bit different from Europe, but you'll find that there's a good community, ESPECIALLY around events like Ocean Week :)

Sidenote: You'll want to make a thread in the [**Team Recruitment**](http://boards.oce.leagueoflegends.com/en/c/team-recruitment) sub-board, as that's probably the more frequented sub-board for people looking for teammates.
Guess Catisfaction will feel at home, considering there is a Wuks in EUW, NA and OCE, will be like they never left.... you clone.
